data.description: Charming open-concept home on a prime lot with no rear neighbors! This functional open floorplan features vaulted ceilings and updated flooring in the living room to perfectly complement any decor. The spacious eat-in kitchen provides plenty of space for meals with loved ones and offers easy access to the extended patio so you can easily enjoy dining al fresco. Retreat to the primary bedroom complete with an elegant tray ceiling and luxurious en-suite bathroom with everything you need to relax and recharge after a long day. You don’t want to miss this one, schedule your showing today before it’s too late!
